node.text: July 7 marks the date of one of; if not the most, shocking moments in wrestling history when Hulk Hogan joined Scott Hall and Kevin Nash as the third man at Bash at the Beach 1996. It was 24 years ago today that the formation of one of the greatest wrestling factions took place. The Outsiders; Scott Hall and Kevin Nash, along side Hollywood Hulk Hogan formed the nWo and the rest is history! Like they say when you're nWo you're  #nWo4life!
